entries.next: Don't have anything else for you right now. But I liked your style. Check back now and again.
entries.cantwork: I never trusted anyone that claimed they could juggle several things at once. Check back when you're not preoccupied.
entries.npc_reset: That's what I get for relying on amateurs. Come back when you're serious about work.
entries.npc_1_1: Hey, pal. I'm looking for a new partner. But I just can't accept anyone. You gotta prove yourself first. My line of work ain't for the timid or the slow-witted. You seem pretty tough to me. Tell you what. If you can make one of my problems go away, I'll consider showing you the trade. You in?
entries.npc_2_1: Nice. The problem's name is Yensi Kolyin and he's a Gran. He didn't have the stomach for the trade and now he wants out. I need you to retire him. I hope I've made myself clear.
entries.npc_3_1: It's always easy to spot the timid and slow-witted. Beat it.
entries.npc_4_1: Piracy is what I'm talking about. Lots of money to be made in that business. But first that problem I was mentioning. You gonna help me take care of it?
entries.npc_backtowork_1: I guess I didn't make myself clear. Don't want to learn the trade, eh?
entries.npc_reward_1: Not bad. But that Gran was pretty easy pickings. I'm not sure if you're trade material. Let me think about it some more. Now get out of here.
entries.npc_work_1: Did you retire that Gran yet? How will you prove yourself a worthy partner if you can't do something as simple as that?
entries.npc_noloc_1: Let me get this loser's coordinates so you can take care of business.
entries.npc_failure_1: Gran are generally pacifists, did you know that? And you couldn't retire one? I think the local cantina needs a barmaid. Beat it.
entries.otherescort_1: I cannot talk now. I'm terribly busy.
entries.dontknowyou_1: I cannot talk now. I'm terribly busy.
entries.npc_breech_1: I knew Dalla the Black would send someone eventually. You are a fool to deal with that murderer.
entries.player_reset_1: I don't want this mission right now.
entries.player_sorry_1: I'll keep working on the mission.
